225
00:15:58,917 --> 00:16:01,878
<font color="japanese">こんな退職金…</c.japanese>

226
00:16:04,255 --> 00:16:06,424
<font color="japanese">最後の最後まで</c.japanese>

227
00:16:07,258 --> 00:16:09,094
<font color="japanese">せんえつながら
誕生日プレゼントです</c.japanese>

228
00:16:09,219 --> 00:16:10,762
<font color="japanese">これで
佐藤さんの好きなものを―</c.japanese>

229
00:16:10,887 --> 00:16:13,264
<font color="japanese">一生 買い続けてください</c.japanese>

230
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,811
<font color="japanese">何も変わってない</c.japanese>

231
00:16:18,728 --> 00:16:21,314
<font color="japanese">むしろ ブレなくてすごい</c.japanese>

